long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A simple extension that allows you to schedule LETSEMA. Meetings.

LETSEMA. is audio and video conferencing solution that provides high quality, scalable video conferences. 

You can try it out yourself at https://meet.letsema.co.ls

This extension provides calendar integrations to schedule meetings for LETSEMA.
